Hellmouth is open source, and patches are appreciated.

Check out the TODO for what you can help on, or get in touch with me.

Folder structure:

/actor: Code for actors (both the player and NPCs).
/actor/ai: Contains the primary AI class and the modules it can call upon.
/data: Contains information about items, skills, etc.
/generators: Procedural content generation code.
/generators/maps: Map generators.
/views: Code for visible UI components (not all of which are View()s)
